# Trained model weights are regenerable by rerunning
# train_pruned_classifiers.py; the metrics/history JSON already capture
# everything meaningful about a run, so the (much larger) weight files
# aren't committed - matching this repo's existing convention of only
# committing small result artifacts (plots, small .npy arrays), not large
# binaries.
